---

<footer class="relative mt-20 overflow-hidden border-t border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800 theme-transition-all">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-80 h-80 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50 animate-float-slow"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative pt-16 pb-12 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
        
        <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-3">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-200 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-white dark:text-zinc-900 text-xl font-bold">JA</span>
            </div>
            <span class="ml-3 text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Portafolio</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            Físico apasionado por la divulgación científica y la educación STEM.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex space-x-4">
            {socialLinks.map(social => (
              <a href={social.href} target="_blank" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <Fragment set:html={social.icon} />
                </svg>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-3">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 pb-2">Explora</h3>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            {navLinks.map(link => (
              <li><a href={link.href} class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-100">{link.text}</a></li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-6">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 relative group overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-3 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.674a3 3 0 01-5.938 0H9.663zM15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2">La Caja de Curiosidad</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-4">
              ¿Tienes una duda sobre física o el universo? Déjala aquí y responderé en mi próximo contenido.
            </p>
            
            <form action="mailto:jerryaneck@outlook.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain" class="space-y-3">
              <textarea 
                name="pregunta" 
                placeholder="¿Por qué el cielo es azul?..." 
                rows="2"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-zinc-500 outline-none transition-all"
                required
              ></textarea>
              <button 
                type="submit" 
                class="w-full py-2 bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-zinc-100 text-white dark:text-zinc-900 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform active:scale-95"
              >
                Enviar mi duda
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 text-center md:text-left">
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">© {currentYear} Jerry Aneck Romero Hernández. Divulgando con pasión.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>